item.title: Toronto may recover from Coronavirus if adult avoid go out
item.description: Abstract: Not only Toronto but the whole world is suffering from the Coronavirus; hence we are thinking about under this challenging situation, is there anything the public can do to reduce the probability of being infected. This paper explores the dataset of COVID-19 Cases in Toronto in 2020, which contains all confirmed and probable cases and is managed by Toronto Public Health since the first case was reported in January 2020.
